name: Attack on S0lst1ce 2021
description:
Pictured: The Skreed Army unleash the Evil Artifact to begin an invasion of Aquaburn during the last day of s0lst1ce 2021, vaporizing a large percentage of the crowd. The Questorians and citizens of Aquaburn will be segregated to Scrambler City as the Skreed occupy the planet.

Artifact Quest Season 3 starts 1.1.22
